flowchart TD
    A[Performance issue detected] --> B{What is the main bottleneck?}
    B -->|Memory shortage / OOM| C[Scale Up first]
    B -->|Concurrent request increase / throughput shortage| D[Scale Out first]
    B -->|Both| E[Scale Up first<br/>Secure per-instance headroom]

    C --> F{Is app stateless?}
    D --> F
    E --> F

    F -->|No| G[Clean up session/file/cache structure]
    F -->|Yes| H{Can dependencies handle it?}

    H -->|No| I[Check DB/Redis/API limits first]
    H -->|Yes| J[Apply Scale Out + Autoscale]

    C --> K[SKU upgrade]
    E --> J
    K --> H

    style A fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#111
    style B fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#111
    style C fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#111
    style D fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#111
    style E fill:#fde68a,stroke:#ca8a04,color:#111
    style G fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#111
    style I fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#dc2626,color:#111
    style J fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#111
    style K fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#111
